三、教學目標 Objectives


金融服務業包括銀行、證券、保險、信托、基金等行業，金融中介機構也包括銀行、證券公司、保險公司、信托投資公司和基金管理公司等。本課程旨在介紹實用的金融業務與金融風險管理之理論與實務，金融風暴說明瞭風險管理在當前的重要性，企業業務改善需要包含改善財務和經營業績、提升競爭優勢。內容包括企業相關交易、ERM(企業風險管理)之分析與設計、產業/公司別之個案分析等，期使同學未來能善用會計資訊的觀念和程序，以協助管理決策和提升競爭力。另外，以簡單易懂的方法，透析金融商品的分解遊戲，讓同學進入有趣的金融操作世界。This course introduces practical financial information and enterprise risk management practices, due to the importance of enterprise risk management is currently in the business to improve enterprise included improving financial and operating performance, reduce losses, enhance competitive advantage. The course includes business-related transaction cycle, internal control and audit enterprise, analysis and design of the ERM, other companies of the case analysis, the future of the so students can make good use of accounting concepts and procedural information to assist management decisions and enhance competitiveness 


 


